Comparison fits of the multiplicative structural mean model

Source: vignettes/compare-smm-fits.Rmd
compare-smm-fits.Rmd
library(OneSampleMR)

Comparison fits

  • Example from the ivtools ivglm() helpfile. First simulate some example data.
set.seed(12345)
n    <- 5000
psi0 <- 0.5
psi1 <- 0.2
Z    <- rbinom(n, 1, 0.5)
X    <- rbinom(n, 1, 0.7*Z + 0.2*(1 - Z)) 
m0   <- plogis(1 + 0.8*X - 0.39*Z)
Y    <- rbinom(n, 1, plogis(psi0*X + log(m0/(1 - m0)))) 
dat  <- data.frame(Z, X, Y)
  • Comparison fit using msmm().
fit02 <- msmm(Y ~ X | Z, data = dat)
summary(fit02)
